# SonarQube workflow

Use **`sonar-scanner`** only to **run analysis and upload** results. Use the **Web API** (e.g. curl) or **Sonar MCP tools** for quality gates, issue search, measures, and issue transitions—not the scanner.

Security hotspots are **not** handled by SonarScanner; use **UI**, **SonarQube for IDE**, or **hotspot endpoints** from your server’s **`/web_api`** if permitted.

Follow **`.agent/workflows/sonarqube-review.md`** for the full process and tool names.

Use **`gh`** only for **GitHub / CI** context (PR checks, workflow runs), not as a Sonar client.
